graph TB
    subgraph "KubeRay Operator (opendatahub namespace)"
        Operator[kuberay-operator<br/>Deployment]
        OperatorMetrics["Metrics Endpoint<br/>/metrics 8080/TCP HTTP"]
        Operator -->|exposes| OperatorMetrics
    end

    subgraph "Optional: KubeRay API Server"
        APIServer[kuberay-apiserver<br/>Deployment]
        RESTEndpoints[REST API<br/>8888/TCP HTTP]
        gRPCEndpoints[gRPC Services<br/>8887/TCP gRPC]
        APIServer -->|exposes| RESTEndpoints
        APIServer -->|exposes| gRPCEndpoints
    end

    subgraph "User Namespace"
        RayClusterCRD[RayCluster CR<br/>ray.io/v1]
        RayJobCRD[RayJob CR<br/>ray.io/v1]
        RayServiceCRD[RayService CR<br/>ray.io/v1]

        subgraph "Ray Cluster (managed by operator)"
            HeadPod["Ray Head Pod<br/>GCS + Dashboard + Client"]
            HeadService["cluster-name-head-svc<br/>6379, 8265, 10001"]
            WorkerPods["Ray Worker Pods<br/>Compute Nodes"]
            Autoscaler["Ray Autoscaler<br/>Sidecar Container"]

            HeadPod -->|exposes| HeadService
            Autoscaler -->|scales| WorkerPods
        end
    end

    User[User/CI] -->|creates| RayClusterCRD
    User -->|creates| RayJobCRD
    User -->|creates| RayServiceCRD

    RayClusterCRD -->|watched by| Operator
    RayJobCRD -->|watched by| Operator
    RayServiceCRD -->|watched by| Operator

    Operator -->|creates/manages| HeadPod
    Operator -->|creates/manages| WorkerPods
    Operator -->|creates/manages| HeadService

    APIServer -.->|REST/gRPC API| Operator

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+]
        ContainerRegistry[Container Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Metrics Collection]
        ObjectStorage[S3/Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    Operator -->|watches/reconciles| K8sAPI
    Operator -->|pulls images| ContainerRegistry
    Prometheus -->|scrapes| OperatorMetrics
    Prometheus -->|scrapes| HeadPod

    WorkerPods -->|connects to| HeadPod
    WorkerPods -->|accesses data| ObjectStorage
    HeadPod -->|accesses data| ObjectStorage

    subgraph "Optional External Integrations"
        IngressController[Ingress/Route<br/>External Access]
        ExternalRedis[External Redis<br/>HA GCS Backend]
        CertManager[cert-manager<br/>TLS Certificates]
        Volcano[Volcano/Yunikorn<br/>Gang Scheduling]
    end

    IngressController -.->|exposes| HeadService
    HeadPod -.->|optional HA| ExternalRedis
    Operator -.->|webhook certs| CertManager
    Operator -.->|batch scheduling| Volcano

    style Operator fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style APIServer fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style HeadPod fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style WorkerPods fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RayClusterCRD fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RayJobCRD fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RayServiceCRD fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style ContainerRegistry fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style ObjectStorage fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
